price: 69. "I had no knowledge of the chiefs (angels) on high when they were disputing and discussing (about the creation of Adam).
arabic: مَا كَانَ لِيَ مِنۡ عِلۡمِۭ بِٱلۡمَلَإِ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰٓ إِذۡ يَخۡتَصِمُونَ
